                <ul class=\"ul\">\r\n                        <li><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>活动时间：2018-10-12&nbsp;-&nbsp;2018-11-09</li>\r\n                        <li><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>活动详情：驴妈妈旅游·成都欢乐谷“万圣欢乐节”</li>\r\n                    <!-- </ul>\r\n                            <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷驴妈妈旅游·成都欢乐谷“万圣欢乐节”\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-10-10/0bc871bf-a9d3-4d6f-83b6-eefb9cca3f0b.jpg\">\r\n                            <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷驴妈妈旅游·成都欢乐谷“万圣欢乐节”\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-10-10/5916cc05-f879-41fa-a460-5c2a71391e21.jpg\">\r\n                            <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷驴妈妈旅游·成都欢乐谷“万圣欢乐节”\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-10-10/c3bfe1fd-100d-48d7-9200-2d03ab6e80b7.jpg\">\r\n                            <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷驴妈妈旅游·成都欢乐谷“万圣欢乐节”\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-10-10/26b391da-844b-490a-89ad-601a29d6d381.jpg\">\r\n                            <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷驴妈妈旅游·成都欢乐谷“万圣欢乐节”\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-10-10/16f9201b-c337-4e12-895a-d8fcea3eff7c.jpg\">\r\n                            <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷驴妈妈旅游·成都欢乐谷“万圣欢乐节”\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-10-10/f0fe6916-7dd6-4281-a7e6-9e5f83324494.jpg\">\r\n                    <hr> -->\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!--精彩活动--结束-->\r\n\r\n    <!--景点介绍--开始-->\r\n    <div id=\"introduction\" class=\"dbox introduction\">\r\n        <div class=\"dtitle\">\r\n            <h2 class=\"dtit\"><i class=\"icon dicon-introduction\"></i>景点介绍</h2>\r\n        </div>\r\n	        <div class=\"dcontent\">\r\n	                <h4>您需要知道的“成都欢乐谷”</h4>\r\n	                <div class=\"introduction-ts\">\r\n	                    <p><em>特色1</em>天地双雄-钢筋之躯高耸云天、气势不凡，带给人们奇妙的惊心之。</p>\r\n	                    <p><em>特色2</em>大摆锤-天地之间独有一番惊心动魄。</p>\r\n	                    <p><em>特色3</em>云霄飞龙-犹如置身翻涌的巨浪之尖，乘风破浪、跌宕起伏。</p>\r\n	                    <p><em>特色4</em>加勒比风暴-抛向高高的浪尖，仿佛随时都会被大海吞没。</p>\r\n	                </div>\r\n	                <ul class=\"ul\">\r\n	                        <li></li>\r\n	                </ul>\r\n	\r\n	            <h4>成都欢乐谷简介</h4>\r\n	            <p>成都欢乐谷占地面积约51万平方米，由阳光港区、欢乐时光区、加勒比旋风区、巴蜀迷情区、飞行岛区、魔幻城堡区、飞跃地中海区、欢乐光年区及丝路传奇区九个主题区组成，融合了丰富多彩的演出剧目。这里，奇观美景目不暇接，扣人心扉；歌舞演艺魅力纷呈，打造都市文化盛宴；大型节庆活动更是激情四射，动感之夜永不谢幕。\r\n</p><p>繁华都市开心地，承载着都市人的欢乐梦想，扬帆起航！</p>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>欢乐时光区</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>绽放嘉年华缤纷光彩。</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷欢乐时光区\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2014-09-24/1411544891670.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>梦幻华侨城</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>狂欢欢乐谷。</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷梦幻华侨城\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2015-05-20/8cecb124-1807-4b01-9342-f945de6819c4.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷梦幻华侨城\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2015-05-20/c4dafc82-0c5c-49e2-a372-79c91669bf30.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷梦幻华侨城\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2015-09-06/b79425aa-5868-4a99-ba69-1c0c83793971.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷梦幻华侨城\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2015-09-06/a2163948-a3ef-4236-a57e-55d96613108f.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷梦幻华侨城\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2015-09-06/3c3e4da0-47b9-4683-8d36-569ae7162722.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>阳光港</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>让欢乐扬帆起航。</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷阳光港\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2014-09-24/1411544813613.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>飞跃地中海区</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>畅享大洋澎湃的激情。</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷飞跃地中海区\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2014-09-24/1411544995110.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>魔幻城堡区</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>迈入童真的奇幻之旅。</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷魔幻城堡区\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2014-09-24/1411545125382.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>巴蜀迷情区</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>踏上惊险的探秘之旅。</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷巴蜀迷情区\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2014-09-24/1411545185153.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>飞行岛区</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>漫游蝶飞鱼翔的世外桃源。</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷飞行岛区\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2014-09-24/1411545241567.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>欢乐光年区</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>穿越时空的欢乐奇幻之旅。</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷欢乐光年区\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2014-09-24/1411545294239.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>丝路传奇</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>从喧嚣的波斯湾集市，到神秘的敦煌飞天，再到千年风蚀的古老卫城和奇妙的卡迪夫绿洲。你将在这里穿过古老的东方城堡、神秘的西亚古城以及浩瀚无垠的沙漠，跟随丝绸之路上的驼队踏上一场极具异域风情的冒险之旅！</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷丝路传奇\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2017-09-01/7c7344b5-470f-40d6-ab17-598ac7c70107.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷丝路传奇\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2017-09-01/1e9bbcf9-0150-498e-9fe1-cb24b195d38e.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷丝路传奇\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2017-09-01/6560989a-e609-4e99-af4e-4585bc278b0d.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷丝路传奇\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2017-09-01/3802c431-5b5e-4111-8e46-5ca3aca684cb.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷丝路传奇\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2017-09-01/c2368c15-3694-492d-a652-37989f145a4e.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷丝路传奇\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2017-09-01/ce3c300d-5765-4da6-ac07-b5a5fa422d10.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                    <h6><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>加勒比水世界</h6>\r\n	                    <p><span class=\"icon dicon-point\"></span>“勇敢者乐园”加勒比海充满了惊险，孕育着无数惊心动魄的浪漫故事。\r\n</p><p>朱利安王子和海伦公主驾着游轮驶向湛蓝的加勒比海，在欢快的海豚成群结队地护航下，开始蜜月之旅。突然，狂风咆哮，滚滚巨浪被掀起，神秘海盗骤然袭来，孤立无援的游轮随时都会遭遇不幸。王子与公主携手并进，率领船员沉着应对，度过了危机，谱写出一段爱的诗章……</p>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷加勒比水世界\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-06-11/5c0e7bc1-7274-4637-8833-248d556e42f6.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷加勒比水世界\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-06-11/11c07be0-5ef1-4933-a1b0-8f0ace4e1968.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷加勒比水世界\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-06-11/9ad7ddb2-e25c-4291-a6cc-52e0bc800f6e.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"imgbox\">\r\n	                                <img width=\"720\" alt=\"成都欢乐谷加勒比水世界\" src=\"http://pic.lvmama.com//uploads/pc/place2/2018-06-11/4133804c-b198-41d3-8d38-3be1e1d7f92b.jpg\">\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"darea noline\">\r\n            <h5>温馨提示</h5>\r\n            <p>1.在不能满足设备安全运行的恶劣天气，无法抗拒的自然灾害情况下（如雷电、雨雪、冰雹、大雾、暴雨、台风等），景区部分项目将临时关闭或部分关闭，表演会取消或部分取消。</p>\r\n            <p>2.严禁倒票，一经发现，相关电子门票作废，入园现场将不予承认，驴妈妈旅游网将不予退费并将相关账号、手机号列入黑名单。请广大用户选择驴妈妈官方网站或官方合作渠道购买，维护自身权益不被侵犯。</p>\r\n            <p>3.景区活动内容如有变动，以当日公告为准。景区所有项目均会定期进行日检、周检、月检和年度检修，相关检修工作可能会造成部分项目运行时间的延迟或暂停对游客开放，详情以景区现场公告为准。</p>\r\n            <p>4.为保障您的出游安全，驴妈妈建议您订购在线支付产品时选购相关旅游保险。</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div><!--景点介绍--结束-->\r\n    <!--交通指南--开始-->\r\n    <a id=\"jtzn\" style=\"font-size:0; padding-top:35px; display:block;\" hidefocus=\"false\"></a>\r\n    <div id=\"traffic\" class=\"dbox traffic\">\r\n        <div class=\"dtitle\">\r\n            <h2 class=\"dtit\"><i class=\"icon dicon-traffic\"></i>交通指南</h2>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"dcontent\">\r\n            <div class=\"traffic-map\" id=\"traffic-map\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; z-index: 0; background-color: rgb(243, 241, 236); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;\"><div style=\"overflow: visible; position: absolute; z-index: 0; left: 0px; top: 130px; cursor: url(&quot;http://api.map.baidu.com/images/openhand.cur&quot;) 8 8, default;\"><div class=\"BMap_mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; top: -130px; z-index: 9; overflow: hidden; user-select: none; width: 700px; height: 390px;\"></div><div style=\"position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 0px; left: 0px; top: 0px; z-index: 200;\"><div style=\"position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 0px; left: 0px; top: 0px; z-index: 800;\"></div><div style=\"position: absolute; height: 0px; width: 0px; left: 0px; top: 0px; z-index: 700;\"><span class=\"BMap_Marker BMap_noprint\" unselectable=\"on\" \"=\"\" style=\"position: absolute; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; cursor: pointer; background: url(&quot;http://api.map.baidu.com/im